scene_description_enriched: A ram stands in profile, facing right, amidst foliage. The ram is depicted with a textured fleece and prominent, curved horns. Behind and around it are stylized leaves and branches, set against a background of stippling. The scene is framed by an arched border with decorative elements at the top corners. The overall impression is of a natural setting, possibly representing a pastoral scene or a symbolic representation of an animal.
